@startuml
title T-Code Access and Authorization Sequence

actor User
participant "Host.Api" as Api
participant "CorrelationIdMiddleware" as Corr
participant "RequestLifecycleLoggingMiddleware" as ReqLog
participant "Authorization Engine" as Authz
database "BusinessDb" as Bdb
database "LogDb" as Ldb

User -> Api: GET /api/tcode/SYS01
Api -> Corr: Attach/Generate CorrelationId
Corr --> Api: CorrelationId ready

Api -> ReqLog: Start request capture
ReqLog -> Authz: Resolve T-Code SYS01
Authz -> Bdb: Query SubModulePage(TransactionCode)
Bdb --> Authz: Page metadata

Authz -> Bdb: Validate Levels 1..6
Bdb --> Authz: Permission set

alt Authorized
  Authz --> Api: Allow + filtered policy
  Api --> User: 200 OK
else Forbidden
  Authz --> Api: Deny reason
  Api --> User: 403 Forbidden
end

ReqLog -> Ldb: Insert http_request_logs
ReqLog -> Ldb: Insert system_logs
ReqLog --> Api: End request capture

@enduml
